[SN]TITLE[SN]
World Snooker Championship 2015 on the BBC

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
BBC Sport will bring you live coverage of the 2015 Snooker World Championship from Saturday, 18 April across BBC TV, Red Button, connected TVs,  online, tablets and smartphones.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Viewers can also watch live coverage of both tables at the Crucible via the BBC Sport website and connected TV. Dedicated streams will be on hand until Thursday, 30 April, when the tournament goes down to a single table.
